Author: WilmaVilma
Text: Lmao not quite the same, but I always bring the same thing to school for lunch. And since it’s literally just fruit people are always like “omg that’s so healthy, I wish I had your ~willpower~ to not bring/get junk food everyday !” Like ma’am it’s not willpower, it’s being down to approximately 7 safe foods in total and having a crippling fear of anything outside of that.  Also all the girls I know have the same “thinspo” as I do. Only difference is that I’m actually going for it lmao. We really do not live in a healthy society
